# app 빌드

# 빌드 방법
@code 
Hyunsoo.kim 김현수님이 작성, 12월 18, 2024에 최종 변경
Git 정보 및 관련 source code download
Clone with SSH
Kaon gitlab log-in  : http://kkms.kaonmedia.com/gitlab/
(Gitlab) Login >> Settings >> SSH Keys >> Add an SSH Key
(PC) 다음과 같이 SSH public key를 생성하고 값을 복사하여 상기 gitlab에 SSH key를 등록 한다.   
- Create an SSH key (leave all options as default)

$ ssh-keygen

$ cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub

K1200UA android main source 
$git clone git@kkms.kaonmedia.com:cjhello/k1200ua/k1200ua.git
kansrc  source code download 
$cd vendor/kaon/K1200UA
$git clone git@kkms.kaonmedia.com:cjhello/k1200ua_vendor/kaonsrc.git
빌드 방법 : 
Android Main Source Build
k1200ua$ source build/envsetup.sh

k1200ua$ lunch

 You're building on Linux >> ubuntu 180.04 or 20.04 사용 권고

 Lunch menu... pick a combo:

K1200UA-eng
K1200UA-user
K1200UA-userdebug
 Which would you like? [aosp_arm-eng]

 

빌드 커맨드는 Git source애 포함되어 있는 build 스크립트를 사용하시면 됩니다.

build script 이용 Build 방법

 1) ./k1200ua_build.sh -c

    : u-boot, kernel, android clean

 2) ./k1200ua_build.sh –m

   : android oem image build

 3) ./k1200ua_build.sh -o

    : include otapackage image

 4) ./k1200ua_build.sh -s

    :  only android build (u-boot, kernel build skip)

 5) ./k1200ua_build.sh -u

    : user mode build



kaonsrc build 방법
a. Kaonsrc code build enable 
$vi vendor/kaon/kaon.mk
TARGET_BUILD_KAON_SRC_BUILD := true
b. edit .gitignore 
.gitignore 파일에서 다음의 부분을 찾아 comment 처리
vendor/kaon/K1200UA/kaonsrc/
android 전체 빌드 시 자동으로 관련 생성 파일 추가
kaonsrc 개별 빌드 방법
개별 빌드 전, 빌드 환경 설정
go K1200UA PDK root directory
$source build/envsetup.sh
$lunch 3
Lunch menu... pick a combo:q
     1. K1200UA-eng
     2. K1200UA-user
     3. K1200UA-userdebug
$cd vendor/kaon/K1200UA/kaonsrc
$mm
생성 파일 위치 
KaonDeviceManager : out/target/product/K1200UA/system_ext/app/KaonDeviceManager/KaonDeviceManager.apk
KaonSystemService : out/target/product/K1200UA/system_ext/app/KaonSystemService/KaonSystemService.apk





@endcode

# Quber 빌드
@code 
Quber packages/middleware  source code 빌드 방법 입니다. 
소스 빌드 하려면 다음의 두개 폴더가 모두 존재 하여야 합니다. 
vendor/quber/packages
vendor/quber/middleware

$source build/envsetup.sh;lunch 3
 
◼ Quber middleware / packages

vendor/quber/packages/pvs
m -j$(nproc) pvsd
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/system/bin/pvsd system/bin/pvsd
 
vendor/quber/packages/StartupService
m -j$(nproc) StartupService
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/system/priv-app/StartupService/StartupService.apk system/priv-app/StartupService/Startu pService.apk
 
vendor/quber/packages/libdhcp/
m -j$(nproc) libdhcp
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/system/lib/libdhcp.so system/lib/libdhcp.so
 
StbApi/StbApi.cpp
m -j$(nproc) libstbapi.system libstbapi.vendor
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/vendor/lib/libstbapi.vendor.so vendor/lib/libstbapi.vendor.so
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/system/lib/libstbapi.system.so system/lib/libstbapi.system.so

$ adb root
$ adb remount
adb push libstbapi.vendor.so vendor/lib/libstbapi.vendor.so
adb push libstbapi.system.so system/lib/libstbapi.system.so
이미지로 빌드시 
cp out/target/product/K1200UA/vendor/lib/libstbapi.vendor.so vendor/quber/prebuilts/packages/libstbapi/
cp out/target/product/K1200UA/system/lib/libstbapi.system.so vendor/quber/prebuilts/packages/libstbapi/
vendor/quber/packages 재거
vendor/quber/middleware 제거
./k1200ua_build.sh -o
 
 
hiddenmenu/pages/HiddenMenuPage.cpp
m -j$(nproc) hiddenmenu
adb push out/target/product/K1200UA/vendor/bin/hiddenmenu vendor/bin/hiddenmenu
cp out/target/product/K1200UA/vendor/bin/hiddenmenu vendor/quber/prebuilts/packages/hiddenmenu/
Z:\K1200UA\k1200ua\vendor\quber\prebuilts\packages\pvs

 
@endcode

# sigining

> [K1200UA_Prodloader_1.0.4.tgz](../data/K1200ua_ATV12/K1200UA_Prodloader_1.0.4.tgz)

@code

HOW TO USE sigining tools -------
 - 2025/09/23 written by LGHV project team

[1] make signing image with unsigned image
$./ota_gen.sh --file /shared/fwimg/K1200UA-ota-00.43.1820.zip

[2] copy signed FW image to custom folde and name
$cp K1200UA-ota.scs_and_arb.signed.zip /shared/fwimg/K1200UA-ota-00.43.1820__usrdbg.signed.zip

[*] signing scripts need python version 2.7 
 - the signing process might be failed if python version is not 2.7xx


  선택       경로              우선순� 상태
------------------------------------------------------------
  0            /usr/bin/python3.8   2         자동 모드
* 1            /usr/bin/python2.7   1         수동 모드
  2            /usr/bin/python3.8   2         수동 모드


@endcode


